data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home that truly defines modern family living. Boasting an additional study/flex room downstairs and a spacious loft on the second floor, there's no shortage of space for family entertainment. Strategically located between Orlando and Tampa, this residence offers easy access to I-4, making your commute a breeze.    The heart of this home is the kitchen, where Quartz countertops, pendant lights over the large island, white 42'' cabinets, a kitchen vent, and stainless-steel appliances create a stylish and functional space. The kitchen is complemented by the inclusion of a water softener, adding a touch of luxury to your daily living.     Oversized sliding glass doors flood the living spaces with natural light and lead to a backyard oasis with no rear neighbors, providing a private retreat for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. The first floor features tile throughout, except for the study-flex room, while wet areas on the second floor are also adorned with tile.    Ceiling fans are strategically placed throughout the home, enhancing comfort and energy efficiency. All bedrooms are conveniently located upstairs, allowing for privacy and separation of living spaces. The laundry room is also situated on the second floor, complete with upper white cabinets for added convenience.    The Master Suite is a haven of luxury, featuring an amazing walk-in closet and double sinks in the bathroom. The elegant open rail for stairs downstairs adds a touch of sophistication to the overall design.    With its thoughtful layout, modern amenities, and prime location, this home is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle. Schedule a showing today and discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience that awaits you in this exceptional property! ( Furnishings can be negotiated!)
